---
title: Fresh Mozz & Prosciutto Lunchbox plus Balsamic Drizzle & Cashew Cranberry Trail Mix
description: For a tasty, casual DIY lunch idea, try our charcuterie-board approach: Creamy fresh mozzarella, luscious prosciutto, and juicy tomato—all served up with a sweet-tangy balsamic drizzle. You can layer it as you choose on the toasty sourdough (or not), add a sprinkle of cashews, pepitas, and cranberries right on top or save the trail mix to enjoy as a sweet and salty end to your lunch. You do you.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fresh-mozz-prosciutto-lunchbox-88fb6ac0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/fresh-mozz-prosciutto-lunchbox-63a0becf588e7912520f3f9c-3cc395cf.pdf
